strace: Traces system calls and signal dispositions.

swindle: Sends emails with forged sender addresses.
switch_root: Switches root file system for a process and its descendants.
sx: Command-line interface to SX client libraries.
symcryptrun, sympow: Symmetric encryption and decryption utilities.
sync, synctex: Synchronizes file system buffers.
syslog2eximlog: Converts syslog format to eximlog format.

sz: Tool to compress or expand files using LZ77/LZ78 compression algorithm.
t1ascii, t1asm, t1binary, t1disasm, t1mac, t1unmac, t50: PostScript and TrueType font conversion utilities.
tabbed.default, tabbed.meta, tabs, tabulate, tac: Text manipulation utilities.
tail: Outputs last part of a file.
tangle: Converts an Emacs org-mode file to a plain text file.
tapestat: Analyzes and visualizes disk usage.
tar, tarcat: Archive and manage files using the tar format.
